snippet.textDisplay: I really hope this is better than Season 1.  I'm a huge fan of the books, and it was so different and confusing I had a hard time following.  I didn't really like Kinneman either.  Kovacs in the books is funnier, and more vicious.  Kimmeman just seemed kinda confused.  This looks like it will be based off book 3, but maybe they are taking a mixed approach?  Might need to re-read them in the mean time.
